# Portfolio Project (cl3menza.com)

## Stack

React + TypeScript + Vite + Framer Motion. Entry: `src/main.tsx`.

## Struktura

- `src/styles/` — modularni CSS: base.css, layout.css, hero.css, sections.css, overrides.css, landing.css
- `src/components/landing/` — LandingScene, LandingHero, LandingBackground, LandingPath, LandingCards, LandingActivation
- `src/components/layout/` — Header, Footer, Layout, Preloader, Ticker
- `src/components/sections/` — HeroCl3menza (aktivan), Hero/HeroNormal/TrustSignals (legacy), Systems, Flagship, AnatomyOfBuild, Process, Stack, Projects, Testimonials, About, Contact
- `src/hooks/` — useCl3menzaBodyClass, useCountUp, useMagnetic (noop), useParallax, useTerminalBoot
- `api/claude.ts` — Vercel serverless function (AI chat backend, van Vite bundle)

## App.tsx

Orkestrira dva moda: **normal mode** (landing) i **cl3menza mode** (dublji sloj).
Normal mode: LandingScene (kontinualni scroll arhitektura).
Cl3menza mode: lazy-loaded sekcije (Systems, Projects, Flagship, AnatomyOfBuild, Process, Stack, Testimonials) via `React.lazy` + `Suspense`. Mount-once pattern (`hasActivated`).
Ulaz: scroll do LandingActivation zone ili CTA button. Izlaz: badge u headeru.

## Typecheck

Dva tsconfig-a:
- `tsconfig.json` → `src/` (moduleResolution: bundler)
- `tsconfig.node.json` → `api/**/*.ts` + `vite.config.ts` (moduleResolution: node)
- Script: `npm run typecheck`

## Build

`npm run build` → Vite prod build, chunked output. `npm run typecheck` → oba tsc prolaze čisto.

## LOCK fajlovi (diraj samo planski, Standard/Strict mode)

- `src/App.tsx` — mode orchestration
- `src/components/landing/LandingActivation.tsx` — scroll-driven cl3 ulaz
- `api/claude.ts` — AI chat handler, rate-limit, validacija

## Conventions

- Zadrži postojeći vizuelni identitet (paleta, tipografija, motion)
- Koristi postojeće CSS klase iz src/styles/ modula (ne global.css — ne postoji)
- Ne uvodi nove dependency-je bez approval-a
- Ne refaktoriši van scope-a

## Do Not

- Menjati dizajn bez approval-a
- Dodavati generic template rešenja
- Praviti nepotrebne abstrakcije
